descriptionHtml:
For me the argonian race is the best race, well except for one thing they look plastic coatet :(

This is my atempt fix fix the spec maps for the male argonian race,
because we all know that bethesda makes them look like plastic... well no more plastic!

They will still have glossy/shiny parts, but now it just looks better :)

This file is ONLY for vanilla body

Also if you want please upload some pictures of your character :)
Keep in mind that the pictures i have uploaded are with ELEFX and Real vision enb combined with skylight enb!
